          },
          "reviewBody": "I will not recommended this school especially for the kids studying in 2-5. \n1. The strenghth is too much high and teachers are not able to focus on each and every child\n2. There is a fashion of unethical evaluation of kids grading them on A, B, C ....etc making them to hate the studies\n3. So called Yogyata khoj are organized just to showcase NEP that they are just doing it\n4. No sports activity as kids school time starts at 08 AM and closes at 11 AM making it roughly 3 hrs of time where most of the kids remain ignored\n5. SUPW classess are taken by maths or science teachers- so that part is also for showcasing\n6. My kid class work copies are mostly marked with incomplete work and most of the pages are colored fully in red colored with heavy notes. The teachers will put all burden on you to teach and complete their work.\n7. Huge fee structure that does not match anywhere with the quality of the education provided to the kids\n8. Music, sports, dance classes are mere jokes and students dont even know who are the teachers attending them\n\n5. ",
